data.description: LOCATION & LAND to call your own. This maintained property has a lot to offer. 2 parcels total 1.4 Acres. The home has hard wood oak floors and updated vinyl flooring. Open livingroom with dining room and kitchen. Kitchen has updated hardwood cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and newer sink, also 4 new windows, 2 decent sized bedrooms, and updated bathroom with walk in shower and built in seat. Solid wood stairs walk up to completely floored bonus room waiting to be finished into large primary bedroom and bath or 2 more bedrooms. Attached 3 season room has plenty of windows, additional freezer remains. Full basement with large Rec room and additional cabinets offering plenty of storage for games/ hobbies. Washer and Dryer will also remain. Attached deep 17X26 Garage with sliding doors leading out to patio. There is also a detached 20X22 garage, and a 14X32 Tuff Shed with overhead door and electric. Black topped U shaped driveway and more! Home is being sold AS IS in an estate.
